HEADWORD: Infrastapedial
<hw>In`fra*sta*pe"di*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Infra</ets> + <ets>stapedial</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to a part of the columella of the ear, which in
many animals projects below the connection with the stapes.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>The infrastapedial part of the
columella.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Infrasternal</ent>⟦br⟧
